rce/Cristian_Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cristian Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristian_Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristian_Medina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the game was interrupted as angry Moroccan fans entered the stadium.\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 463, \"end\": 471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998895680225, \"rank\": 1.1042545620054879e-07, \"text\": \"Moroccan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The match was temporarily suspended and after almost two hours, a VAR check confirmed that the goal was ruled out because of offside.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 565, \"end\": 568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4590868977281214e-26, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The remaining three-plus minutes were played as players re-emerged in an empty stadium.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The match ended 2-1 win in favour of Morocco, sparking a reaction from Messi on social media.\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 760, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999813051093, \"rank\": 1.8684298176112254e-08, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://